
 Capture your opponents pieces and turn them over to your
 color. Get control over majority of the board to win.  
 
 KNOWN issue
 The following games did not work due to a missing 
 "org.kde.games.core" module error:

    "knetwalk"
    "kbreakout"
    "kreversi"

 On Debian based systems it is sufficient to install the 
 "qml-module-org-kde-games-core" package from the repository
 to solve this issue.
 
 SITE: https://userbase.kde.org/Applications/Games
